SUMMARY:Salsa & Bachata Night @ Komana Brewery in Cary 
DESCRIPTION:Raleigh & Triangle Activities Meetup Group\n🔥 Join us EVERY
  WEDNESDAY for a fun night of Salsa & Latin dancing! 🔥\n\nCome early—
 doors open at 7:15 PM for a meet & greet mixer\, then jump into the action
  with our dance lessons!\n\n🍻 Dance • Drink • Connect\n\n💃 Salsa
  & Bachata Lesson | 7:30–8:30 PM\nBeginner-friendly • No partner neede
 d\n\n🎁 Stick around for a chance to win free door prizes after the less
 on!\n\n🕺 Social Dancing | 8:30–11:30 PM\n🎧 DJ Giovanni spinning Sa
 lsa\, Bachata & Latin hits\n\n🔥 Drink specials all night!\n\n❄️ Air
 -conditioned venue\n🪩 Spacious dance floor\n\n💲 $10 B4 9pm (Early bi
 rd special)\n$15 after 9pm!\n\n📍 KōMANA Brewing Co. 1020 Ryan Rd\, Car
 y\, NC\n\n🚗 Free parking\n🔞 18+ to party | 21+ to drink\n\nGrab your
  friends and make Wednesdays your favorite night of the week! 💃🕺\n[F
 ollow us on fb ](Facebook.com/salsa4lifenc)\nFollow us on fb Salsa4lifenc 
 or instagram salsa4life_com
