SUMMARY:Free Medieval Combat Training (Durham\, NC) - Broadsword - Armor -
  Rapier
DESCRIPTION:Raleigh & Triangle Activities Meetup Group\nLearn the European
  martial art of broadsword and shield\, wearing steel armor. Or maybe Rena
 issance dueling with rapier and dagger is more your style. Beginners welco
 me! No experience necessary. Some loaner armor is available.\n\nRapier ins
 tructor: Percival Aldridge\, OD\, OP\nBroadsword instructor: William of Be
 dford\, KSCA\nAdministrator (KM): Charles Fleming\n*This event is held and
  managed by the [Canton of Buckston-on-Eno](https://buckston.windmastershi
 ll.org)\, a branch of the* [Society for Creative Anachronism\, Inc.](https
 ://welcome.sca.org/) *and is considered the Official channel of this group
  here. Questions regarding its content should be directed to [chatelaine@b
 uckston.windmastershill.org](http://chatelaine@buckston.windmastershill.or
 g) or to [socialmedia@sca.org.](http://socialmedia@sca.org.) Inclusion of 
 external links does not indicate implicit nor explicit endorsement of any 
 content or products.*
